Àtụ:Infobox musical artist
Rachel Akosua Funmilola Garton (nke a maara dị ka Lola Rae; amụrụ na 20 Jenụwarị 1991) bụ onye na-agụ egwu Naijiria

Ọ nwetara nkwadọ̀ mgbe a tọhapụrụ egwu izizi ya "Watch My Ting Go", nke nwetara otuto dị egwu ma si otú a mee ka a họpụta ya maka Most Promising Female Act to Watch na 2013 Nigeria Entertainment Awards.
A mụrụ Lola Rae n'aka nna onye Britain na nne onye Ghana na Obalende, mpaghara Lagos, Nigeria
Ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ praịmarị na sekọndrị na St

Saviour's School, Ikoyi; na Lekki British International High School, Lagos, n'otu n'otu. Otú ọ dị, ọ hapụrụ Naịjirịa gaa England mgbe ọ dị afọ iri na ise iji mezue agụmakwụkwọ mahadum ya na Central Saint Martins, ebe ọ gụrụ akwá ejiji.
Ọrụ ntụrụndụ Lola Rae malitere dị ka onye na-agba egwú mgbe ọ bụ onye otu egwu egwu "Mystikal" n'afọ 2010

Ndị na-agba egwú Mystikal nyochara maka Britain's Got Talent ebe Rae bụrụ abụ na asọmpi ahụ ma onye ọka ikpe Simon Cowell họpụtara ndị na-agba egwu Mystikal na ọkara ikpeazụ nkè asọmpi ahụ. Na ngwụcha asọmpi ahụ, a bịanyere aka na Syco maka otu afọ
Rae jụrụ oku ọ kpọrọ The X Factor iji chụsoo ọrụ onwe ya dị ka onye na-agụ egwu.

N'abalị iri na itoolu n'ọnwa Nọvemba n'afọ 2012, Rae wepụtara egwu izizi ya bụ Watch My Ting Go na egwu ọzọ akpọrọ High. A họpụtara ya dị ka "Most Promising Female Act to Watch" na 2013 Nigeria Entertainment Awards
Vidio ya na "Watch My Ting Go" gosipụtara na Soundcity TV na 8 Jenụwarị 2013 na ngosipụta cameo site na Iyanya na Emma Nyra. A họpụtara vidiyo ahụ na 10th Channel O Music Video Awards.

N'ịgbaso "Watch My Ting Go", Rae gosipụtara Iyanya na egwú akpọrọ Fi Mi Le nke mere ka a họpụta ya ọzọ na 2014 Nigeria Entertainment Awards. O mere ihe ngosi dị ka mmasị ịhụnanya Ice Prince na vidiyo egwu ya "More".
Na Mee 2018, Rae mụrụ nwa nwanyị.
